title: The London Promenade Orchestra: Reader's Digest: Candlelight Cla
description:
The World's Most Beautiful Melodies
The London Promenade Orchestra
Eric Hammerstein, Conductor

1. Greensleeves (Traditional)
2. Air for the G String (Bach)
3. Barcarolle from The Tales of Hoffmann (Offenbach)
4. Evening Prayer from Hansel and Gretel (Humperdinck)
5. Intermezzo from Intermezzo (Provost-Henning)
6. Ave Maria (Schubert)
7. The Girl With The Flaxen Hair (Debussy)
8. Vocalise (Rachmaninoff)
9. Londonderry Air (Traditional; arranged by Leibowitz)
10. La Ci Darem La Mano from Don Giovanni (Mozart)
11. Plaisir d'Amour (Martini)
12. Serenade (Schubert)
13. Liebestraum (Dream of Love) (Liszt)
14. Vissi d'Arte from Tosca (Puccini)
15. My Heart At Thy Sweet Voice from Samson and Delilah (Saint-Saens)
16. Depuis le Jour from Louise (Charpentier)
17. Ave Maria (Bach-Gounod)
18. Un Bel Di from Madama Butterfly (Puccini)
19. Vesti la Giubba from I Pagliacci (Leoncavallo)
20. On Wings of Song (Mendelsohn)
21. Flower Song from Carmen (Bizet)
22. Evening Star from Tannhauser (Wagner)
23. Lullaby (Brahms)
